{"tid":2102741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法庭表明不會接納涉案警員的證供，裁定被告襲警罪名不成立。","createTime":"2020-07-10T16:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T17:21:32.000Z","uid":230104,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c18effb6b2d6aff7fddbdb2c1aead846091fb8ee","tid":2102741,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:43:19.000Z","msg":"被告被指於去年11月12日在西灣河犯案，他否認襲警罪受審，案件早前僅花半天便審結。裁判官何俊堯裁決指，警員供詞有多處疑點，惟控方均沒作跟進，例如閉路電視片段可見案中警員甫接近被告便制服他，與他們供稱曾表露身份及多次警告的說法不符；另外，若警員沒作出不當行為，被告不會求警員別傷害他。法庭表明不會接納涉案警員的證供，裁定被告襲警罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200710/ZFASY3ZI4BLXBIO77V7ETQDDLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2FZFASY3ZI4BLXBIO77V7ETQDDLQ%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=4dcd402e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2FZFASY3ZI4BLXBIO77V7ETQDDLQ%2F&h=ae458e4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200710/ZFASY3ZI4BLXBIO77V7ETQDDLQ/</a>"},{"pid":"800961471ded27f6f7902bdc5eeff600590477e1","tid":2102741,"uid":312758,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"好快，又少個正常裁判官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7444e2c182df0a53f77ac0739b3ee368eb6f1c46","tid":2102741,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"白衫狗死全家"},{"pid":"4ed718f6b9fcc85f0ffbeb4c316857ffe72e842f","tid":2102741,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:49:48.000Z","msg":"個細路坐左幾日?<br />\n定有得保?"},{"pid":"a6d288e72909bbd93a7e86b7334dc2255b3b5e23","tid":2102741,"uid":264245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:49:54.000Z","msg":"呢單live哂出街，本來都擔心比狗官當睇唔到照判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bac38a5b3ab3544bfa0f309f1187e91339